# Firebase Admin credentials

Use **`FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON`** (entire service account JSON) on Railway — same as `mobile/docs/push-notifications.md`.

Do **not** split into `FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID` / `FIREBASE_CLIENT_EMAIL` / `FIREBASE_PRIVATE_KEY` on hosted envs.

```typescript
const serviceAccount = JSON.parse(process.env.FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON!);
admin.initializeApp({ credential: admin.credential.cert(serviceAccount) });
```
